        {
            "title": "華僑銀行憂油價難下 或削港今年增長預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"華僑銀行憂油價難下 或削港今年增長預測\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/p0m93hgVFIccmShUMk0etw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/38cd2780-28a5-11f1-b2df-706419a24430\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">華僑銀行憂油價難下 或削港今年增長預測</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
